Class AnyTreeTableModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inqwell.any.client.AnyTreeModel
      • com.inqwell.any.client.AnyTreeTableModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeTableModel, EventListener, CellEditor, CellEditorListener, TreeCellEditor, TreeCellRenderer, TreeModel

    public class AnyTreeTableModel
extends AnyTreeModel
implements TreeTableModel
    An extension of the standard Inq AnyTreeModel that provides implementations for use as a TreeTable.
